## 5. IMPLEMENTATION PRIORITIES

### MVP Scope (Hackathon)

#### Priority 1: Core Eligibility + WhatsApp (MUST HAVE)
- âœ… Scheme database (5 schemes)
- âœ… Eligibility matching algorithm
- âœ… WhatsApp bot integration (Twilio)
- âœ… Basic NLP using Bedrock Claude
- âœ… HTML form fallback for testing

#### Priority 2: SMS + Documentation (SHOULD HAVE)
- âœ… SMS notifications (AWS SNS)
- âœ… Document checklist generation
- âœ… Enrollment center locator (hardcoded for Lucknow)
- âœ… Real-world testing with 5 users

#### Priority 3: Tracking + Analytics (NICE TO HAVE)
- â±ï¸ Application status tracking
- â±ï¸ Dashboard for users to view their applications
- â±ï¸ Reminder system (can be manual SMS for MVP)
- â±ï¸ Analytics dashboard (conversion, engagement)

